OL,7,FITV Border journalist Jack Currie
OL,8,Fspoke with Carlisle United Sporting
OL,9,FDirector Rob Clarkson
OL,11,FCarlisle United's Sporting Director
OL,12,FRob Clarkson is aiming to emulate
OL,13,Fprevious success he has had and help
OL,14,Flift the Blues away from potential
OL,15,Frelegation out of the football league.
OL,17,FClarkson has been brought in to assist
OL,18,Fmanager Mike Williamson through the
OL,19,Frole of Sporting Director.
