OL,3,CRob Clarkson aims to emulate
OL,4,CManchester City and Rangers success at
OL,5,CBrunton Park
OL,7,FHe has previously worked at clubs
OL,8,Fincluding Manchester City and Rangers
OL,9,Fand is looking to use his skills
OL,10,Flearned in those roles into his new
OL,11,Fone at Brunton Park.
OL,13,FSpeaking about the job he will be
OL,14,Fdoing in Cumbria, Clarkson said: "The
OL,15,Fkey elements that I will be looking
OL,16,Fafter is the recruitment, the coaching
OL,17,Fstaff, the medical team, analysis and
OL,18,Fthe academy.
OL,20,F"It is a big role, it is a broad role,
OL,21,Fbut it is one that I am enjoying."
