OL,3,CRob Clarkson aims to emulate
OL,4,CManchester City and Rangers success at
OL,5,CBrunton Park
OL,7,FAnd Clarkson said it was an obvious
OL,8,Fdecision for him to join the Blues.
OL,10,FHe said: "Size of club, fanbase and
OL,11,Fthen the ambition.
OL,13,F"So the owners were very clear from
OL,14,Fthe outset when I met them, where they
OL,15,Fwant the club to be. That was really
OL,16,Fexciting for me, particularly as a
OL,17,Ffirst time Sporting Director it is
OL,18,Falways important that you chose the
OL,19,Fright club and right ownership."
