OL,7,FClarkson spent many seasons at
OL,8,FManchester City and undertook a number
OL,9,Fof roles during his time at the club.
OL,11,FHe learned from many top coaches
OL,12,Fduring his time there including Pep
OL,13,FGuardiola and Mikel Arteta.
OL,15,FHe said: "I had five years there and I
OL,16,Fdid a lot, worked with a lot of really
OL,17,Fgood people and good coaches and some
OL,18,Ftop talent.
