OL,3,CRob Clarkson aims to emulate
OL,4,CManchester City and Rangers success at
OL,5,CBrunton Park
OL,7,F"I straightaway saw an elite
OL,8,Fenvironment and how that looks on and
OL,9,Foff the pitch. I like teams to play
OL,10,Ffrom the back, through midfield, be
OL,11,Fexciting and good to watch.
OL,13,F"That was always the type of way I
OL,14,Fliked to play as a player, playing in
OL,15,Fyouth teams and then going to
OL,16,FManchester City and my jobs since then
OL,17,Fas well.
