OL,3,CRob Clarkson aims to emulate
OL,4,CManchester City and Rangers success at
OL,5,CBrunton Park
OL,7,F"It is important to me that we play a
OL,8,Fcertain way that matches what the
OL,9,Fowners want and what the manager wants
OL,10,Fas well."
OL,12,FClarkson then moved onto Rangers where
OL,13,Fhe became Head of Domestic Scouting
OL,14,Ffor the club, leading a team in charge
OL,15,Fof all transfers involving British
OL,16,Fclubs.
OL,18,FDuring his time there he played a key
OL,19,Frole in the signing of Joe Aribo, Glen
OL,20,FKamara and Calvin Bassey. All players
OL,21,Fwho were sold on for a big profit.
