OL,3,CRob Clarkson aims to emulate
OL,4,CManchester City and Rangers success at
OL,5,CBrunton Park
OL,7,FHe said that he wants to follow the
OL,8,Fsame formula at Carlisle United.
OL,10,FHe said: "We want to invest and to
OL,11,Ffind assets and younger players that
OL,12,Fare developing and improving and we
OL,13,Fget them at the right point and then
OL,14,Fthey can really develop with us.
OL,16,F"Clearly we can see that we are not
OL,17,Fscoring enough goals so therefore we
OL,18,Fneed to create more and score more.
OL,19,FThat would suggest the top end of the
OL,20,Fpitch whatever that would look like."
